#: kded/kded.cpp:128
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Inotify Instance Capacity Low"
msgstr "Låg kapasitet på Inotify-instansar"

#: kded/kded.cpp:131
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"You have too many applications wanting to monitor file changes! When the "
"capacity is exhausted it will prevent further file monitoring from working "
"correctly. Either close some applications or increase the limit. Currently "
"using %1% of instances and %2% of watches."
msgstr ""
"Du har for mange program som ønskjer å overvaka filendringar. Når "
"kapasiteten er oppbrukt, vil ikkje vidare filovervaking fungera skikkeleg. "
"Du må anten lukka nokre program eller auka grensa. Brukar no %1 % of "
"instansane og %2 % av overvakingane."

#: kded/kded.cpp:138
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"You have too many applications wanting to monitor file changes! When the "
"capacity is exhausted it will prevent further file monitoring from working "
"correctly. Your capacity cannot be increased. Try closing some applications "
"to recover additional resources. Currently using %1% of instances and %2% of "
"watches."
msgstr ""
"Du har for mange program som ønskjer å overvaka filendringar. Når "
"kapasiteten er oppbrukt, vil ikkje vidare filovervaking fungera skikkeleg. "
"Du kan ikkje auka kapasiteten. Prøv å lukka nokre program for å frigjera "
"ressursar. Brukar no %1 % of instansane og %2 % av overvakingane."

#: kded/kded.cpp:145
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action"
msgid "Increase Instance Limit"
msgstr "Auk instansgrensa"

#: kded/kded.cpp:152
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Inotify Watch Capacity Low"
msgstr "Låg kapasitet på Inotify-overvakingar"

#: kded/kded.cpp:155
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Your open applications want to watch too many files for changes! When the "
"capacity is exhausted it will prevent further file monitoring from working "
"correctly. Either close some applications or increase the limit. Currently "
"using %1% of instances and %2% of watches."
msgstr ""
"Dei opna programma ønskjer å overvaka for mange filer for filendringar. Når "
"kapasiteten er oppbrukt, vil ikkje vidare filovervaking fungera skikkeleg. "
"Du må anten lukka nokre program eller auka grensa. Brukar no %1 % of "
"instansane og %2 % av overvakingane."

#: kded/kded.cpp:162
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Your open applications want to watch too many files for changes! When the "
"capacity is exhausted it will prevent further file monitoring from working "
"correctly. Your capacity cannot be increased. Try closing some applications "
"to recover additional resources. Currently using %1% of instances and %2% of "
"watches."
msgstr ""
"Dei opna programma ønskjer å overvaka for mange filer for filendringar. Når "
"kapasiteten er oppbrukt, vil ikkje vidare filovervaking fungera skikkeleg. "
"Du kan ikkje auka kapasiteten. Prøv å lukka nokre program for å frigjera "
"ressursar. Brukar no %1 % of instansane og %2 % av overvakingane."

#: kded/kded.cpp:169
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action"
msgid "Increase Watch Limit"
msgstr "Auk overvakingsgrensa"
